@startuml
title State Machine: Vehicle Status

[*] --> Available
Available --> Assigned : assign to officer
Assigned --> InUse : officer checks out
InUse --> Assigned : officer returns
InUse --> Maintenance : issue reported
Assigned --> Available : reassignment

Available --> Maintenance : scheduled service
Maintenance --> Repair : issues found
Repair --> Maintenance : fix incomplete
Repair --> Available : repairs complete
Maintenance --> Available : service complete

InUse --> OutOfService : major failure
Assigned --> OutOfService : safety concern
OutOfService --> Repair : repair authorized
OutOfService --> Retired : beyond repair

Available --> Reserved : future assignment
Reserved --> Assigned : assignment time
Reserved --> Available : reservation cancelled

Retired --> [*]

note right of Maintenance
  Regular servicing
  Inspection
  Cleaning
  Equipment check
end note
@enduml
